[@tg626](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/112361-tg626/) DMagic's [flexo docking tubes](https://spacedock.info/mod/838/Flexible%20Docking) have a different module [FlexoTube], requiring an additional <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> code segment to give them sounds. I tried it out and it works seamlessly with flexotubes docking both with each other and standard ports.

    @PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[FlexoTube],!MODULE[DPSoundFX]]:FOR[DPSoundFX]
    {MODULE{	name = DPSoundFX	sound_docking = FP_DPSoundFX/Sounds/dock	sound_undocking = FP_DPSoundFX/Sounds/undock	internalSoundsOnly = false}
    }
